body:
(SKIP this part if you don&#039;t want to read a mini rant) So, lets be real the community in league of legends sucks, I mean its why so many people have left the game to play others (myself included), however I do enjoy the game, I just can&#039;t stand games that aren&#039;t with a 5 man, as generally you will have at least one troll in the game (for either team), making the game purely boring and tedious to play. Since nearly all of my friends have already uninstalled league, I need some new people to add onto my friends list to game with! (rant over)

So if you are a relaxed player, doesn&#039;t matter if you are bronze 5 and have a 3 percent win rate, just if you wanna chill and have some genuinely fun games feel free to add me and we can organise to play some games sometime! hopefully will see you on the fields of justice, summoners.
